(a,b)=1,n
\displaystyle \left(a+b,{a^n+b^n\over a+b}\right)\mid n.
\displaystyle \left(a+b,{a^n+b^n\over a+b}\right)=d
\displaystyle d\mid {a^n+b^n\over a+b}=(a+b)^2(a^{n-3}-a^{n-4}b\dots+b^{n-3})-2ab(a^{n-3}\dots+b^{n-3})-ab^{n-2}
d\mid (a+b)
d=1
(a,b)=1
a+b
a^kb^{n-k}\equiv (-1)^kb^n
n=\frac{a^n+b^n}{a+b}+(\ldots)\cdot (a+b)
 \frac{a^n+b^n}{a+b}=a^{n-1}-a^{n-2}b+a^{n-3}b^2\mp\cdots -ab^{n.2}+b^{n-1}\equiv n
